- **Expected Results:** Sample cardiac discharge simplification with benchmarks[0m[0m
- **The Honest Take:** Segmentation matters more than model choice, readability validation catches drift, entity preservation prevents scary bugs, caching pays for itself[0m[0m
- **Variations:** Multi-language, interactive reading level adjustment, EHR-integrated triggers[0m[0m
